name: Multifaceted Gratitude Reflections
description: By Travis LeRoy Southworth | @travisleroy | "Gratitude Reflections" (2021), 2550 x 3000px. This digital painting is part of my series "Thresholds" where I create works partly through a GAN and my own computerized brush strokes. Released as part of the "OBJKT4OBJKT 2" event on April 23rd, 2021.
